# Pipeline run logs — stdout transcripts (progress chatter + false-start/killed runs).
# Redundant with the real provenance: per-fit convergence/timing live in the fit JSONs
# (results/fits/**, experiments/*/results/**) and environment/git SHA in run_manifest.json.
# Kept locally for debugging; not version-controlled.
results/logs/

# Experimental / non-abstract models kept out of the shared repo.
# WARNING: the package imports through this folder via __path__ (e.g.
# dataset.py -> observers.models.online_switching_observer), so a clone that
# lacks it cannot `import observers.api`. Only safe once those load-bearing
# modules are moved back into observers/ proper.
other models/
